  "keyFeatures": [
    "Clean Architecture layers: Domain, Application, Infrastructure, Web",
    "CQRS pattern via MediatR with pipeline behaviours (validation, logging, authorization, performance)",
    "Multiple client framework options: Angular, React, or Web API only",
    "Multiple database providers: SQLite (default), PostgreSQL, SQL Server via Entity Framework Core",
    ".NET Aspire for local orchestration, observability, and self-contained testing",
    "ASP.NET Core Identity with JWT authentication",
    "FluentValidation for request validation",
    "Scalar API documentation (OpenAPI)",
    "Comprehensive test suite: unit, functional, integration, and acceptance tests"
